data.description: Welcome to 4732 Eldon Ct located in beautiful Kempsville Lake! This updated, large end unit townhome, boasts 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and 1 car garage. The oversize primary bedroom is bright and airy with a lake view. The 2 additional bedrooms are both spacious. Desirable open floor plan showcase the beautiful kitchen. Large patio can accommodate any outdoor gatherings. Roof is approx. 1 yr, HVAC approx. 1 yr, vinyl siding approx. 10 yr, all new granite countertop, newer kitchen appliances, new floors throughout the home. Premier location near VB Town Center, military bases, beach, local attractions and 264. Schedule your tour today!
